Controversial Dutch filmmaker shot dead on Amsterdam street byStephanie van den Berg(ADDS filmmaker's quotes)
Dutch filmmaker Theo van Gogh, who had received threats over acontroversial film he made about Islam, was shot and stabbed to deathTuesday while cycling on an Amsterdam street, officials said.
Dutch politicians and commentators were united Tuesday in theircondemnation of the murder, in broad daylight on an Amsterdam street,of controversial filmmaker Theo van Gogh and called for calm togetherwith representatives of the Dutch Muslim community.
Theo van Gogh, a Dutch filmmaker and writer who had recently made atelevision film critical of Islam, was shot and stabbed to death onan Amsterdam street on Tuesday.
